snippet.title: Relationship Rules + Your Fear is a LIAR - Lunch at the Loft
snippet.description:
In episode 3 of Lunch at the Loft Koereyelle and LB are reminding your that your fear is a liar! It will keep you complacent and playing it safe never leads to success!

Get the inspiration and motivation you need to fight fear and find faith! 

Tune in LIVE each Thursday at 12NOON EST [Periscope @SingleWivesClub] For more visit TheSingleWivesClub.com
